{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/19446768.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-19446768"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "We can also consider Blaze:\n\n* https://code.google.com/p/blaze-lib/", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>We can also consider Blaze:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.google.com/p/blaze-lib/\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://code.google.com/p/blaze-lib/</a></li>\n</ul>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-07-02T09:56:07.312794+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 19446768}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/26283279.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-26283279"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "There is some discussion on the fcl issue tracker about using eigen:\n\n* https://github.com/flexible-collision-library/fcl/issues/96", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>There is some discussion on the fcl issue tracker about using eigen:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/flexible-collision-library/fcl/issues/96\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://github.com/flexible-collision-library/fcl/issues/96</a></li>\n</ul>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2016-03-16T21:17:33.228829+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 26283279}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/34127030.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-34127030"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "I'm closing the analogous Gazebo issue now that Gazebo math has been fully deprecated in favor of ignition math. Please consider the discussions on that issue as well, there are a lot of nice comments there:\n\nhttps://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/issues/929/consider-using-eigen-to-improve-math", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I'm closing the analogous Gazebo issue now that Gazebo math has been fully deprecated in favor of ignition math. Please consider the discussions on that issue as well, there are a lot of nice comments there:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/issues/929/consider-using-eigen-to-improve-math\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/issues/929/consider-using-eigen-to-improve-math</a></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-02-02T17:22:15.546158+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 34127030}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/38860971.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-38860971"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "cc @mxgrey", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>cc @mxgrey</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-08-03T00:22:45.229870+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 38860971}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/38861207.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-38861207"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "I definitely think using `Eigen` would add a lot of value to `ignition::math`, and simultaneously `ignition::math` would add a lot of value to Eigen. This would likely result in a much broader adoption and larger community for `ignition::math`, even going beyond the robotics community.\n\nThe tricky part is that `Eigen` structures are not easy to wrap or extend due to the implementation details of their templates. We would need to be very smart about how we interface with `Eigen` and how we approach incorporating it into the larger goals of `ignition`. I personally believe the added difficulty would be very much worthwhile in the long run, but I think there are reasonable arguments to be made against it.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I definitely think using <code>Eigen</code> would add a lot of value to <code>ignition::math</code>, and simultaneously <code>ignition::math</code> would add a lot of value to Eigen. This would likely result in a much broader adoption and larger community for <code>ignition::math</code>, even going beyond the robotics community.</p>\n<p>The tricky part is that <code>Eigen</code> structures are not easy to wrap or extend due to the implementation details of their templates. We would need to be very smart about how we interface with <code>Eigen</code> and how we approach incorporating it into the larger goals of <code>ignition</code>. I personally believe the added difficulty would be very much worthwhile in the long run, but I think there are reasonable arguments to be made against it.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-08-03T00:35:56.428644+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 38861207}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/38861269.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-38861269"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "Maybe we could start with a companion package called `ignition-math-eigen` that provides conversion functions back and forth between ignition and eigen types. For now, this would keep `ign-math` free of an eigen dependency. Since DART uses eigen, it wouldn't be a big leap to have gazebo depend on `ignition-math-eigen` if DART is found.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Maybe we could start with a companion package called <code>ignition-math-eigen</code> that provides conversion functions back and forth between ignition and eigen types. For now, this would keep <code>ign-math</code> free of an eigen dependency. Since DART uses eigen, it wouldn't be a big leap to have gazebo depend on <code>ignition-math-eigen</code> if DART is found.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-08-03T00:44:30.288534+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 38861269}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/38861339.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-38861339"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "Helper functions would definitely be good if we decide not to use `Eigen` natively. I'm somewhat of the opinion that, if we're going to change the underlying math library, then we should make that decision as soon as possible to minimize the overhead of making that change (but of course the most important thing is to make a *good* decision rather than a hasty one).", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Helper functions would definitely be good if we decide not to use <code>Eigen</code> natively. I'm somewhat of the opinion that, if we're going to change the underlying math library, then we should make that decision as soon as possible to minimize the overhead of making that change (but of course the most important thing is to make a <em>good</em> decision rather than a hasty one).</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-08-03T00:53:33.394013+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 38861339}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/38861569.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-38861569"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "Switching to `Eigen` is a big change, so I thought a baby step with `ignition-math-eigen` would give us a taste of the packaging difficulties before jumping in all the way. We could consider it part of the decision-making process.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Switching to <code>Eigen</code> is a big change, so I thought a baby step with <code>ignition-math-eigen</code> would give us a taste of the packaging difficulties before jumping in all the way. We could consider it part of the decision-making process.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-08-03T01:22:14.366411+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 38861569}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/38861608.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-38861608"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "Honestly, the packaging is completely trivial compared to the challenge of making it the native basis data structure. We could even just pull the Eigen headers into the `ign-math` repo if we wanted to make it literally 100% trivial, although I'd strongly prefer making it an external dependency, because that users can benefit from the latest revisions without us needing to keep our copy of Eigen's source tree up to date.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Honestly, the packaging is completely trivial compared to the challenge of making it the native basis data structure. We could even just pull the Eigen headers into the <code>ign-math</code> repo if we wanted to make it literally 100% trivial, although I'd strongly prefer making it an external dependency, because that users can benefit from the latest revisions without us needing to keep our copy of Eigen's source tree up to date.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-08-03T01:26:18.159473+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 38861608}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/38861645.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-38861645"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "I agree that changing the native basis data structure is a huge challenge, but that doesn't mean we should ignore packaging, since I expect that will be a source of concern when adding a dependency to a package that currently doesn't have any. By packaging, I also include updating documentation of installation instructions and CI scripts. I mean, I think it's worth doing anyway even if we don't make the big switch, and getting our feet wet with packaging will be work we'd have to do anyway if we make the big switch.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I agree that changing the native basis data structure is a huge challenge, but that doesn't mean we should ignore packaging, since I expect that will be a source of concern when adding a dependency to a package that currently doesn't have any. By packaging, I also include updating documentation of installation instructions and CI scripts. I mean, I think it's worth doing anyway even if we don't make the big switch, and getting our feet wet with packaging will be work we'd have to do anyway if we make the big switch.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-08-03T01:31:41.128316+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 38861645}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/39352325.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-39352325"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "I've noticed that there are some (almost certainly unintentional) inconsistencies in the APIs provided by Vector2, Vector3, and Vector4 as alluded to in pull request #181. This kind of thing naturally occurs in code with a [WET](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don%27t_repeat_yourself) anti-pattern.\n\nI think the ideal solution to this is to implement these classes using template arguments for the number of components, similar to the way Eigen does. The thing is, at that point we'll be on the path to reimplementing a less-developed version of Eigen, so we'd be better off just using Eigen wholesale.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I've noticed that there are some (almost certainly unintentional) inconsistencies in the APIs provided by Vector2, Vector3, and Vector4 as alluded to in <a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/pull-requests/181/adding-non-const-bracket-operators-and\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #181</a>. This kind of thing naturally occurs in code with a <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don%27t_repeat_yourself\" rel=\"nofollow\">WET</a> anti-pattern.</p>\n<p>I think the ideal solution to this is to implement these classes using template arguments for the number of components, similar to the way Eigen does. The thing is, at that point we'll be on the path to reimplementing a less-developed version of Eigen, so we'd be better off just using Eigen wholesale.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-08-25T20:00:04.875894+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 39352325}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/39352544.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-39352544"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "I still think that conversion functions in a separate `ignition-math-eigen` package would be a good first step.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I still think that conversion functions in a separate <code>ignition-math-eigen</code> package would be a good first step.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-08-25T20:17:44.968552+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 39352544}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/46903742.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-46903742"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "The use of eigen is not on our roadmap right now. This might change in the future, but for now there are more important features and issues to tackle.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The use of eigen is not on our roadmap right now. This might change in the future, but for now there are more important features and issues to tackle.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-07-24T12:40:49.246526+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Nate Koenig", "uuid": "{c862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:095b1e12-74ed-4e20-b44f-2f0745b616e0/ca24bb11-4787-4b14-a20d-d91835e9bde2/128"}}, "nickname": "Nathan Koenig", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:095b1e12-74ed-4e20-b44f-2f0745b616e0"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 46903742}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/46910317.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-46910317"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "@nkoenig eigen would allow a nice way to handle 2d simulation with similar data structures. Is it possible to keep eigen as a build dependency for ign-physics but only use ignition-math types in the API that faces ign-gazebo?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>@nkoenig eigen would allow a nice way to handle 2d simulation with similar data structures. Is it possible to keep eigen as a build dependency for ign-physics but only use ignition-math types in the API that faces ign-gazebo?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-07-24T17:33:33.627420+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 46910317}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/46914747.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-46914747"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "Here is some more explanation about my concerns.\n\nI get the value proposition of eigen, but I need to weigh it against the implementation cost and our obligations. Right now the cost is high relative to the value. Gazebo has worked for 16 years without eigen, no one is banging at our door for 2d simulation, and we have high risk features to implement.\n\nWe will get to eigen integration, but it can't happen right now. Importantly, I don't want to be in the situation where we have inconsistencies between the ignition libraries. I'd like the ignition libraries to be curated by us, and reflect a consistent and purposeful design. \n\nWe can revisit eigen after we are in good place with gazebo11's core features. This will likely be sometime middle of next year.\n\nWe can leave eigen as a build dependency.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Here is some more explanation about my concerns.</p>\n<p>I get the value proposition of eigen, but I need to weigh it against the implementation cost and our obligations. Right now the cost is high relative to the value. Gazebo has worked for 16 years without eigen, no one is banging at our door for 2d simulation, and we have high risk features to implement.</p>\n<p>We will get to eigen integration, but it can't happen right now. Importantly, I don't want to be in the situation where we have inconsistencies between the ignition libraries. I'd like the ignition libraries to be curated by us, and reflect a consistent and purposeful design. </p>\n<p>We can revisit eigen after we are in good place with gazebo11's core features. This will likely be sometime middle of next year.</p>\n<p>We can leave eigen as a build dependency.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-07-24T21:40:51.093053+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Nate Koenig", "uuid": "{c862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:095b1e12-74ed-4e20-b44f-2f0745b616e0/ca24bb11-4787-4b14-a20d-d91835e9bde2/128"}}, "nickname": "Nathan Koenig", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:095b1e12-74ed-4e20-b44f-2f0745b616e0"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 46914747}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19/comments/46914884.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19#comment-46914884"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/issues/19.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 19, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}ts=1533305"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-math", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-math", "uuid": "{18503e50-08ea-4d88-ab99-110fde3c7256}"}, "title": "Consider using eigen"}, "content": {"raw": "I should note that you are more than welcome to use eigen if it doesn't effect a public API.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I should note that you are more than welcome to use eigen if it doesn't effect a public API.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-07-24T21:58:50.333688+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Nate Koenig", "uuid": "{c862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:095b1e12-74ed-4e20-b44f-2f0745b616e0/ca24bb11-4787-4b14-a20d-d91835e9bde2/128"}}, "nickname": "Nathan Koenig", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:095b1e12-74ed-4e20-b44f-2f0745b616e0"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 46914884}], "page": 1, "size": 16}